here, ride it all the way up.

00:29:01.860 --> 00:29:04.740
But never forget that
there's going to be a bubble.

00:29:04.740 --> 00:29:06.300
There is always a bubble.

00:29:06.300 --> 00:29:10.170
In every innovation wave so far,
there's always been a bubble.

00:29:10.170 --> 00:29:13.440
