which don't disappear.

00:29:54.370 --> 00:29:57.240
You just go on to the
next innovation wave.

00:29:57.240 --> 00:30:02.070
This is the way economies grow,
through these innovation lives.

00:30:02.070 --> 00:30:05.360
So it's a pretty
important concept.

00:30:05.360 --> 00:30:10.080
