00:37:49.560 --> 00:37:50.910
And it's his Nobel Prize talk.

00:37:50.910 --> 00:37:53.730
So for economics writing,
it's fairly accessible.

00:37:53.730 --> 00:37:57.893
But even then, it's not simple.

00:37:57.893 --> 00:37:59.310
If you're going
to be reading it--

00:37:59.310 --> 00:38:01.470
and I'm going to ask everybody
