I'm pretty sure, like, energy,
nuclear [INAUDIBLE] It's just

01:15:39.790 --> 01:15:42.478
like, you know, there's
a lot of empty kitchens

01:15:42.478 --> 01:15:44.020
that are the most
important problems.

01:15:44.020 --> 01:15:45.790
But also, from the
capitalist perspective,

01:15:45.790 --> 01:15:47.300
it's like, you want a monopoly.

01:15:47.300 --> 01:15:48.700
So it's the place
you want to be.

01:15:48.700 --> 01:15:52.360
If you discover fusion,
