01:18:28.707 --> 01:18:29.790
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN: Right.

01:18:29.790 --> 01:18:30.290
And, look.

01:18:30.290 --> 01:18:34.050
If we could get
energy onto the wave,

01:18:34.050 --> 01:18:36.120
it would make all
the difference.

01:18:36.120 --> 01:18:38.250
We could do it, all right?

01:18:38.250 --> 01:18:41.177
So if we could manage to
get it into this phase--

01:18:41.177 --> 01:18:43.260
and we're not, we're still
in the build up phase--

01:18:43.260 --> 01:18:47.957
but if he could get here, that's
gets to be really interesting.

