01:19:15.312 --> 01:19:16.020
But you're right.

01:19:16.020 --> 01:19:18.300
The technological advances
that could actually

01:19:18.300 --> 01:19:21.330
scale this thing, actually now,
I think, for the first time,

01:19:21.330 --> 01:19:23.970
appear in sight,
become plausible.

01:19:23.970 --> 01:19:25.230
Still a long term project.

01:19:25.230 --> 01:19:30.310
But I think we're a lot closer
than we were a decade ago.

