01:19:44.650 --> 01:19:46.420
And I've had some
conversations like this.

01:19:46.420 --> 01:19:49.858
And I'm always sort of prone
to think about the values

01:19:49.858 --> 01:19:52.150
that we promote as a society,
both in the United States

01:19:52.150 --> 01:19:55.120
and across the world, in the
societies that they propagate,

01:19:55.120 --> 01:19:58.030
